data.description: This Bellevue Blvd multi-level is the best deal in the Fontanelle Hills area. This home has two beautiful living spaces as well as several flex areas that can be used as additional offices, sitting areas, etc. This unique split floor plan features a generously sized primary bedroom on the upper level and two additional bedrooms below.  The lowest level features a giant walk out living space, storage, and a nonconforming bedroom. So much room to spread out both inside and out!  The secluded backyard is serene. Home sits on 1/3 acre. This home has had many renovations in the last few years including: roof (2022), exterior paint (2023), all new gutters and downspouts (2023), carpet (2022), new sliding door for walkout basement (2023) plus more.  All appliances stay with the home.
